data.title: Jesse Birdsall - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Jesse Birdsall: his birthday, what he did before fame, his family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Famous for his roles on the BBC1 soap operas Eldorado (as Marcus Tandy) and Hollyoaks (as Fraser Black), he is also notable for his portrayal of Nick Beckett in the action and sci-fi series Bugs.

Before Fame

Early in his career, he appeared in a youth cooking show hosted by Nanette Newman and made an uncredited appearance in a 1980 episode of the TV series Minder. His breakthrough role was in the 1984 miniseries Annika.

Trivia

He made two guest-star appearances in Midsomer Murders.

Family Life

The child of the internationally famous graphic designer Derek Birdsall, he spent his youth in London, England. His marriage to actress Gwyneth Strong began in 2000 and produced two children.
